Richard Davies (American actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Richard_Davies_(American_actor) 0 Richard Davies (1915–1994) was an American actor.Davies was born in Provo, Utah. His first films date from 1941, and he was active through the early 1960s, ranging from lead roles to small bit and character parts.
